le close encounter and\nmodels with multiple encounters (as common in mergers). The main limiting\nfactor at present seems to be the accuracy of elemental abundances and lack of\ndirect observations at different galactocentric radii to the Sun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jun 2014 20:50:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jun 2014 21:03:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Jun 2014 02:02:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-26"}
