usion\nof the direct Pauli reduction produces small increases in its violation.\nResponse functions which depend on the transverse current are sensitive to the\nlower component of relativistic wave functions, and hence, would provide a\nmeasure of the appropriateness of any relativistic model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jun 2014 04:52:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2016 12:50:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2016 22:40:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-03"}
